BuyMadeEasy
E-Commerce website 
⚡ Scalable Django-Based API for Modern Online Shopping
🌟 Overview

This project is a production-ready E-Commerce backend system built with Django, designed to handle real-world shopping workflows efficiently.

It focuses on clean architecture, scalability, and performance, making it suitable for enterprise-level applications and backend engineering roles.

🧠 Core Highlights

✨ Modular Architecture (apps-based structure)
⚡ High-performance API design
🔐 Secure authentication system
📦 Efficient product & order management
🧩 Easily extendable & production-ready

🛠️ Tech Stack
Layer	Technology
Backend	Django
API Layer	Django REST Framework
Database	SQLite (Dev) / PostgreSQL (Production)
Tools	Git, GitHub

🚀 Features
🔐 Authentication
User Registration & Login
Secure password handling
🛍️ Product Management
Product listing
Category-based filtering
Product detail APIs
🛒 Cart System
Add / Remove items
Dynamic cart updates
📦 Order System
Order creation
Order tracking (extendable)
